@startuml Sequence_PageLoad
title Feature 09 - Dashboard SSR Page Load

actor Browser
participant "Next.js Server\n(RSC)" as SSR
participant "tRPC Server\nCaller" as TRPC
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Browser\n(Hydration)" as Client

Browser -> SSR : GET /dashboard\n(with session cookie)

SSR -> SSR : Validate session\n(middleware)

SSR -> TRPC : dashboard.getSummary()
SSR -> TRPC : dashboard.getSavingsChart()
SSR -> TRPC : dashboard.getPendingActions()
SSR -> TRPC : dashboard.getRecentActivity()

TRPC -> DB : SELECT metrics,\nactions, activity
DB --> TRPC : Result sets

TRPC --> SSR : Hydrated data

SSR -> SSR : Render server components\n(MetricCards, layout)
SSR -> SSR : dehydrate() React Query\nstate for client

SSR --> Browser : Streamed HTML\n+ dehydrated state\n+ JS bundles

Browser -> Client : Hydrate React tree
Client -> Client : HydrationBoundary\nrestores React Query cache
Client -> Client : Mount client components\n(SavingsChart, PendingActions)
Client -> Client : Subscribe to SSE\n(/api/events)

note right of Client
    Charts render immediately
    from dehydrated data.
    No loading spinners.
end note

@enduml
